Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class ChannelVisualization

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.VisualizationObject
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.ChannelVisualization
public class ChannelVisualization extends VisualizationObject
ChannelVisualization creates the visualizations for the channel analysis of the WARP program. Nomrally this method is private but is maade public for testing purposes.

CS2820 Spring 2024 Project: Implement this class to create the file visualization that is requested in Warp.

1.7
